expect.help:
Please note that it's possible that you will not be able to retrieve certain combinations of metrics and pivots due to limitations of LinkedIn's API. Unsupported combinations will be represented by metrics returned as equal to 0 despite the fact that the affected metrics are higher than 0 in LinkedIn's web UI.

For example, you cannot pivot by `Campaign` and `Conversion` and get `Clicks`. Clicks would come out as 0 in this case.
